      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>HMT and BEIS commissioned the City of London Corporation on 24 November 2020 to establish an independent taskforce to boost socio-economic diversity in UK financial and professional services.</p>

<p>For more information on the taskforce, please contact: <a href="mailto:socio-economicdiversity@cityoflondon.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">socio-economicdiversity@cityoflondon.gov.uk</a></p>
</div>

</div>
